reviewText: Achtung! The "Cahiers du Cinema" can't even put the right film on the DVDs . On this two disks package the first film is correctlly :"La Vie des mortts." by Desplechin But the second disk is not :" La Sentinelle" as indicated on the cover, but "Sauvage innocence" By Garrel..... What a joke But what can you expect from these pseudo-intellectuels?
